<html
	xmlns:c = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/core"
	xmlns:e = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/entity"
	xmlns:i18n = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/i18n"
	xmlns:md = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/md"
	xmlns:string = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/string"
	xmlns:html = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/html">
	<head>
		<title>XTML Documentation - string:truncate</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>string:truncate</h1>
		<p>This tag will truncate a string to your desired length.</p>
		<p><e:lt/>string:truncate value="Shorten this string to 16 characters" length="16" /<e:gt/> will result in</p>
		<p><string:truncate value="Shorten this string to 16 characters" length="16" /></p>
		<p><e:lt/>string:truncate length="16"<e:gt/>Shorten this string to 16 characters<e:lt/>/string:truncate<e:gt/> will result in</p>
		<p><string:truncate length="16">Shorten this string to 16 characters</string:truncate></p>
	</body>	
</html>